    "content": "\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">University tutor &#8211; From $70 for 1 hour or $115 for 2 hour session with private tutor at your location in Sydney</h4>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Firstly, university study can be very demanding and <a href=\"https://headspace.org.au/blog/majority-of-aussie-students-stressed-depressed/\">distressing</a>, hence the demand for a university tutor.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s no surprise that 70 percent of university students are distressed due to the challenge of balancing study with other concerns such as work etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hence, Boldtutor offers the best private tutor at a great price, easing your stress in the process.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Furthermore, booking with Boldtutor helps us support a great cause &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.four-paws.org.au/\">Four Paws Animal Welfare </a>charity.</p>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What Boldtutor offers:</h5>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Private university tutor starting from 1 hour including online tutoring</li><li>Location of your choice in Sydney</li><li>Help with Bachelor of Arts, Bachelor of Education, etc</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contact us</h5>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Visit <a href=\"http://boldtutor.com.au/university-tuition-sydney/\">Boldtutor</a> for more information about our university tuition service</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to also check out our university <a href=\"http://boldtutor.com.au/money-back-guarantee-university-tuition-assignment-help/\">money back guarantee </a>for assignment help</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Call or message us on Whatsapp &#8211; +61416419270</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Email us &#8211; contact@boldtutor.com.au</p>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Snapshots of success</h5>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out our snapshots of success gallery below to see the results our university clients have achieved.</p>\n\n\n\n[Best_Wordpress_Gallery id=&#8221;24&#8243; gal_title=&#8221;university results&#8221;]\n",
    "date": "2020-07-10T13:59:25",
