    "content": "\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Every fifth 2 hour private tutor session you book with Boldtutor in Sydney is half price. Terms and conditions apply.</h4>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<p>Every fifth 2 hour private tutor session you book with <a href=\"https://boldtutor.com.au/\">Boldtutor</a> at your desired location in Sydney is half price.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Boldtutor rewards loyal clients. That is why every fifth 2 hour private tutor session you book with me in Sydney is half price.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This offer applies to clients booking 2 hour tutoring services for high school English, <a href=\"https://educationstandards.nsw.edu.au/wps/portal/nesa/resource-finder/hsc-exam-papers/2019/english-advanced-2019-hsc-exam-pack\">English HSC</a>, Modern History, Society and Culture, English language and University tuition.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have any further questions about this offer, please contact Boldtutor on:</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>0416419270 &#8211; You can contact me on WhatsApp as well</strong></li><li>Alternatively, you can send an email &#8211; <strong>contact@boldtutor.com.au</strong></li></ul>\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terms and Conditions</h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Only applicable to clients based in Sydney, NSW</li><li>Applicable only to clients booking at least a 2 hour private tutor session</li><li>Only applicable to clients booking a private tutor session for high school English, English HSC, Modern History, Society and Culture and University tuition</li><li>Not applicable for clients booking a University assignment help session</li><li>The offer is redeemable when the client books their fifth session. For example, after four paid sessions, the client&#8217;s fifth session will be half price. The same applies to the client&#8217;s 10th session and so on.</li><li>Boldtutor reserves the right to end this offer at any time.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
